{"tid":560754,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)情人節節目","createTime":"2018-02-14T11:23:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-14T14:50:11.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2ee92b41d603a04f0549c41ae1d2619631b38efe","tid":560754,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T11:23:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=IPoT2sBkZHYG%2FgHshpWVTP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=38daa7b3\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=IPoT2sBkZHYG%2FgHshpWVTP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=aee5ea2a\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.inmywordz.com/uploads/20170203161133_88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.inmywordz.com%2Fuploads%2F20170203161133_88.jpg&h=fa78c43f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/bd/Begin_Again_film_poster_2014.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fbd%2FBegin_Again_film_poster_2014.jpg&h=7bbaf839&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/b6/Sing_Street_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fb6%2FSing_Street_poster.jpg&h=8cf9c8ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.什麼都好的ok男，遇見了精靈古怪的肛門期女孩(超潔癖、一絲不苟)，在彼此擁有的500個日子裡，所有的&ldquo;愛愛&rdquo;奇招，都為這段感情注入了無限火辣的熱情元素，像是淋浴性愛、床上床下、IKEA展示間的激情挑逗等，夏天的手臂也變成了湯姆的畫布，這些都在湯姆的心裡留下深深的愛戀痕跡，他已經認定了夏天就是這輩子要廝守的伴侶&hellip;不過，夏天卻不認為作愛等於戀愛，他倆又將如何面對500天後全新的開始呢? <br />\n<br />\n2.Dan Mulligan (馬克&middot;魯法洛 飾) 曾是一間成功的唱片公司高層，住在紐約市，他跟他的妻子Miriam Hart (凱薩琳&middot;堅娜 飾) 分居了，並勉強在轉變中的音樂行業中掙扎求存。被解僱後的他，他繼續暴飲酗酒，使他來到東下城的酒吧，並在那裡遇到Greta James (綺拉&middot;奈特莉 飾)..<br />\n<br />\n3.1985年，都柏林南部內城區，萊勒一家面臨著諸多生活問題。主教勞勃（埃丹&middot;吉倫 飾）苦惱於他的建築實踐和婚姻，靠酗酒和狂抽菸支撐精神。在家庭會上，他宣布為了省錢，要把小兒子康納（福迪亞&middot;瓦爾什-匹羅）從學費高昂的學校轉到免費的公辦學校辛格街CBS（Synge Street CBS）。他表示兩家學校的水平相當。哥哥布倫丹（傑克&middot;雷諾）嘲笑他轉學還有家庭的狀況...<br />\n<br />\n7 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=IPoT2sBkZHYG%2FgHshpWVTP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=dd0beabf\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=IPoT2sBkZHYG%2FgHshpWVTP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=6b329002\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07870a38027226d066735559c2730bfa90a6d18a","tid":560754,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T11:57:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e6904c2d3b1b2e7357dfc353f822e7497496034","tid":560754,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T12:47:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c7533e32047dd6217e830bfa3894829ce259f5","tid":560754,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T13:18:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b76a391db695e79ea8bb81114b9b5df73a27b08d","tid":560754,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T14:10:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"208819849c9bb48c0433d42b1604a80537e269ec","tid":560754,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T14:44:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69901e3b808bef32bb2e182d343793502c029072","tid":560754,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T14:50:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}